<head>
  <style>
    /* Styling for the Transaction Tracker header */
    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem; /* Adjust the font size */
      font-weight: bold; /* Make the header bold */
      text-align: center; /* Center align the header */
      color: #3B1E54; /* Set a deep color for the header */
      margin-top: 50px; /* Add top margin for spacing */
    }

    /* Styling for the paragraph description */
    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem; /* Set the font size */
      color: #333; /* Dark grey color for better readability */
      text-align: center; /* Center align the paragraph */
      max-width: 800px; /* Limit the width for readability */
      margin: 20px auto; /* Center the paragraph and add margin for spacing */
      line-height: 1.6; /* Increase line height for better readability */
      padding: 0 15px; /* Add padding for responsive design */
    }
    /* Custom purple button styling */
.btn-purple {
  background-color: #6f42c1 !important; /* Purple background */
  border-color: #6f42c1 !important; /* Purple border */
}

.btn-purple:hover {
  background-color: #5a2d9b; /* Darker purple on hover */
  border-color: #5a2d9b; /* Darker purple border on hover */
}

.text-white {
  color: white !important; /* Ensure text is white */
}
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>Transaction Tracker</h1>
  <p>It is your personal finance management tool that helps you stay on top of all your financial transactions. Whether you're tracking income, expenses, or investments, this platform offers an easy-to-use interface to help you organize and monitor your transactions efficiently.</p>

<!-- Button container -->
<div class="button-container text-center">
  {{#if user}}
    <a class="btn btn-purple btn-lg text-white mx-3" href="#">{{user.username}}</a>
    <a class="btn btn-purple btn-lg text-white mx-3" href="/logout">Logout</a>
  {{else}}
    <a class="btn btn-purple btn-lg text-white mx-3" href="/register">Register</a>
    <a class="btn btn-purple btn-lg text-white mx-3" href="/login">Login</a>
  {{/if}}
</div>
</body>
